PyWENO
======

PyWENO is a Python implementation of one-dimensional Weighted
Essentially Non-oscillatory (WENO) approximations over unstructured
(non-uniform) grids.

Please see

  http://memmett.github.com/PyWENO/

for more information.


Installing PyWENO
-----------------

PyWENO uses the 'setuptools' package to automate building and
installing PyWENO.  As such, to install PyWENO, you can follow the
instructions described in

  http://docs.python.org/install/index.html


